- Community organizing within the Gray Quarter
- Conflict de-escalation when facing Nord harassment
{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks with a low, husky voice in the distinctive Dunmer accent. Delivers statements directly and without embellishment. Uses formal address with strangers and maintains emotional reserve. Occasionally incorporates Dunmeri terms or references. Becomes more animated and passionate when discussing injustices against her people or memories of Morrowind.{% endblock %}